# cargo-fuzz private artifacts (corpus + crash inputs) — these are generated
# at fuzzing time and persist locally. They are uploaded by the nightly CI
# workflow only on failure (see .github/workflows/fuzz-nightly.yml) and the
# `fuzz-corpora` branch carries the long-lived corpus per Phase 9 plan.
